    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game features various enemies and characters from other NecroCatic Games' releases such as &quot;The Tower of Wowers&quot;, &quot;CarsFuckingDragons&quot; and &quot;Grand Strokers&quot; in a brand spankin' new adventure! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It has some throw back maps and is a stand alone game set in the NecroCatic World. We hope you enjoy!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features : </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•Two dozen different characters to recruit and find!! You may recognize some of them! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•Tons of enemies and bosses to fight hand-drawn by Cesare from Italy! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•A digital metric poop ton of armor and weapons to collect! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•Traditional turn-based combat with new and clearly superior <strong>Retro Sideview Combat</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•Open World Exploration with many maps!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•Another Dragon Strip Club!! You read that right! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•Day/night cycle with the hour, day, week, month and even year!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•In-game weather system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•Chase events...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And more...</p>",
